data.description: An amazing custom-built home in the heart of Fountain city. With over 3000 sqf of living space. This Gem sitting on an almost half acre lot with a flat private back yard, offering 4 beds/bonus, 3 baths. Huge primary room with sitting area and a large bath with walk-in shower, whirlpool and double vanities. Two large guest rooms, full bath, office, laundry and a large bonus on the second floor with dual staircases. All new paint and carpet.  Living, family and dining rooms are interacting with each other and also an additional full bath are on the first level. Kitchen with an island, pantry and breakfast nook are in corresponding with dining and living rooms. All stainless appliances are less than two years old.  Beautiful back patio can accommodate all family and friend's gatherings with a warm atmosphere because of the fireplace and fire pit. The extra-large double car garage has plenty of room for a workshop. Just minutes from shopping, grocery, parks and medical offices. This is move in ready so schedule your private showing now.
